than the ice on this lake.

27
00:02:49,570 --> 00:02:50,310
Yuwen Yue.

28
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:54,890
At first,

29
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:57,390
I simply wanted to get out

30
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,280
and live my own life.

31
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:04,490
Later, I met Yan Xun

32
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:07,180
and heard from him about Yanbei.

33
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,490
I felt my heart

34
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:11,900
starting to beat again.

35
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,550
I realized

36
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:17,090
I was born for a reason.

37
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,670
Maybe

38
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,650
that was my fate.

39
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:31,010
Unfortunately,

40
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,660
my dream was shattered

41
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:43,240
because I overestimated myself.

42
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,890
I thought I was capable enough

43
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,030
to make a difference

44
00:03:50,170 --> 00:03:51,670
and protect others.

45
00:03:56,850 --> 00:03:58,010
Eventually,

46
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:01,250
I realized

47
00:04:02,690 --> 00:04:03,660
there wasn’t much I could do

48
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:04,810
on my own.

49
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:10,390
My friends and relatives

50
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:14,640
left me one by one.

51
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,440
I failed to protect them,

52
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:22,410
and many others…

53
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:25,200
Died because of me.

54
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,080
I’m not a good leader.

55
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:36,750
Xiuli Army didn’t have any belief

56
