but they believed in me.

57
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:42,280
But I was the one

58
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,700
who put them into wars and danger

59
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,250
over and over,

60
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,740
causing them to shed blood and die.

61
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,880
The peaceful life

62
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,070
I promised them

63
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:58,640
never comes true.

64
00:05:01,580 --> 00:05:03,290
I saved their lives once.

65
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,480
I should not be so selfish

66
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,010
to let them fight for me.

67
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:20,760
If...

68
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,810
I mean if...

69
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,800
If I had obeyed Yan Xun’s order

70
00:05:30,010 --> 00:05:31,780
and expelled Xiuli Army from Yanbei,

71
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:36,160
then many of them

72
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,680
would not have died.

73
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,020
They would have still been alive.

74
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,940
Do you regret it?

75
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:00,840
I’ve been through a lot.

76
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,040
