77
00:06:05,010 --> 00:06:06,230
I have done so much

78
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:07,860
and come this far.

79
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,750
I’ve made mistakes, too.

80
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:15,610
