81
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:17,870
I have never had regrets

82
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,680
because I always follow my heart.

83
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:25,100
I just...

84
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,460
I just feel tired.

85
00:06:39,210 --> 00:06:40,390
If you are tired,

86
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,650
then stop

87
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,890
and take a break.

88
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,990
That way, you’ll be able

89
00:06:49,450 --> 00:06:50,840
to move forward.

90
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,380
Roma wasn’t built

91
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:55,720
in a day.

92
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,790
Even without Cheng Yuan,

93
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:01,240
there’d be someone else.

94
00:07:03,650 --> 00:07:04,290
What do you picture

95
00:07:04,290 --> 00:07:05,510
Yanbei is like?

96
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,420
That everyone is loyal and brave?

97
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,820
That everyone is looking forward

98
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,490
to your return?

99
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,710
Where there are people,

100
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,900
there are disputes.

101
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:29,650
