183
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,840
His Highness was an

184
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,080
innocent man.

185
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:53,000
But what happened on the Jiuyou Platform

186
00:12:53,780 --> 00:12:55,010
has changed him

187
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:56,270
tremendously.

188
00:12:58,260 --> 00:12:59,760
Things would never go

189
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,400
as we wished.

190
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,550
My concern is

191
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,350
if this continues,

192
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:07,980
we’ll be even further

193
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,020
from our original aspiration.

194
00:13:12,300 --> 00:13:13,590
People change.

195
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,630
Achu, you know what?

196
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,850
I realize

197
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:20,970
the soldiers I see

198
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:25,150
patrolling in the streets

199
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:26,890
are not those

200
00:13:26,890 --> 00:13:27,700
I know anymore.

201
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:30,410
It occurred to me

202
00:13:32,310 --> 00:13:33,750
that those I knew

203
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,500
had either died in battles,

204
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:38,910
or left Yanbei.

205
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:40,680
Maybe

206
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:43,190
it’s time for me

207
00:13:43,190 --> 00:13:44,080
to leave as well.

208
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:49,710
I understand how you feel.

209
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,860
I was in the same position as you were.

210
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:57,090
I witnessed

211
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:58,730
his hatred and pain.

212
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,280
I witnessed

213
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,140
his suffering.

214
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:05,040
We, as bystanders, could never

215
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,720
understand those feelings.

216
00:14:08,090 --> 00:14:09,290
Everyone has the right

217
00:14:09,290 --> 00:14:10,960
to choose how to live their lives.

218
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:13,390
It’s his choice.

219
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:16,030
I disagree with it,

220
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,030
but

221
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:21,590
I respect it.

222
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,110
Our decisions are not

223
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:26,240
always right,

224
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:29,350
but they aren’t always wrong either.

225
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:33,060
But there are principles

226
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:34,830
that we need to follow.

227
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:37,470
We can’t be partners,

228
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:39,440
but

229
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,790
we won’t be enemies either.

230
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:47,110
In this

231
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:49,530
chaotic time,

232
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:51,200
except for freedom

233
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,380
and love,

234
00:14:54,070 --> 00:14:55,230
I’ll only risk my life

235
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:56,210
to keep

236
00:14:57,410 --> 00:14:58,370
my faith.

237
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,310
And that

238
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,930
has already become

239
00:15:04,930 --> 00:15:05,810
part of the plateau of Yanbei.

240
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:13,920
Zhong Yu.

241
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,170
Maybe we should go together.

242
00:15:23,530 --> 00:15:24,900
