243
00:15:26,570 --> 00:15:30,360
Achu. His Highness can

244
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,870
rule the world

245
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,480
and conquer

246
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,000
every piece of land.

247
00:15:35,410 --> 00:15:36,620
