248
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:38,120
he can do whatever it takes

249
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,300
to destroy everything

250
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:40,000
that stands in his way.

251
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:42,890
But you’re different.

252
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,470
He can’t do anything about you.

253
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:51,400
Achu.

254
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:54,890
Don’t give up on him.

255
00:15:56,280 --> 00:15:58,080
Only you can save him now.

256
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,330
Think about those days.

257
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,660
Think about how he struggled

258
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:05,110
to come this far.

259
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:07,310
Think about his suffering.

260
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:09,760
Don’t let hatred

261
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,850
blind him.

262
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,460
Don’t let bastards

263
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:13,470
like Cheng Yuan

264
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,250
succeed.

265
00:16:22,060 --> 00:16:23,120
Before you leave,

266
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,950
could you do me a favor?

267
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:27,890
I’d like to meet with Mr. Wu.

268
00:16:31,730 --> 00:16:32,600
Mr. Wu.

269
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:45,140
Chu Qiao. We’ve finally met.

270
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:47,380
It is quite difficult

271
00:16:47,690 --> 00:16:49,160
