278
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:05,170
When Ms. Bai Sheng killed herself

279
00:17:05,170 --> 00:17:06,360
on the Jiuyou Platform,

280
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:08,050
when Yan Xun was nearly killed

281
00:17:08,050 --> 00:17:09,870
during those three years in Chang’an,

282
00:17:09,870 --> 00:17:11,830
and when he set Chang’an on fire,

283
00:17:11,830 --> 00:17:13,320
when the war was on,

284
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:14,610
